  "title": "Declassification Threshold Shift",
  "concept": "Institutions hold information secret until the strategic cost of secrecy exceeds the risk of disclosure—then the threshold flips and what was once protected becomes public.",
  "interactiveId": "0067229a-4b98-4a1a-8f7e-a62e5beac72a",
  "sourcePieceId": "f074806a-4711-420b-a275-b27efc4c3ed1",
  "publishedAt": 1778379170834,
  "voiceScore": 90,
  "content": {
    "type": "html",
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>Declassification Threshold Shift</title>\n<style>\n  :root {\n    --bg: #faf7f1;\n    --fg: #1a1a1a;\n    --muted: #6b6b6b;\n    --line: #e5e0d6;\n    --gold: #c9a227;\n    --teal: #1a6b62;\n    --red: #c92727;\n  }\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body {\n    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 20px;\n    color: var(--fg);\n    background: var(--bg);\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  h2 {\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin: 0 0 4px;\n  }\n  p.subhead {\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .control {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 14px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n  }\n  .control label {\n    font-weight: 500;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .control input[type=range] {\n    flex: 1;\n    accent-color: var(--teal);\n    min-width: 120px;\n  }\n  .control output {\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    min-width: 4ch;\n    text-align: right;\n  }\n  .scales {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 20px;\n    margin: 24px 0;\n  }\n  .scale {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 8px;\n  }\n  .scale-label {\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.06em;\n    margin-bottom: 2px;\n  }\n  .bar-track {\n    height: 28px;\n    background: var(--line);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .bar-fill {\n    height: 100%;\n    transition: width 200ms ease-out, background-color 200ms ease-out;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-size: 0.8rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #fff;\n  }\n  .threshold-line {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 0;\n    bottom: 0;\n    width: 2px;\n    background: var(--fg);\n    left: 50%;\n    transform: translateX(-1px);\n    opacity: 0.3;\n  }\n  .threshold-label {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: -20px;\n    left: 50%;\n    transform: translateX(-50%);\n    font-size: 0.7rem;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  }\n  .decision {\n    margin: 18px 0 6px;\n    padding: 12px 16px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 2px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    font-size: 0.95rem;\n    transition: border-color 200ms ease-out;\n  }\n  .decision.released {\n    border-color: var(--teal);\n  }\n  .decision strong {\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  p.caption {\n    margin: 14px 0 0;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .scales {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h2>Drag the slider to move forward in time</h2>\n<p class=\"subhead\">Watch how the balance between secrecy risk and disclosure cost shifts over decades.</p>\n\n<div class=\"control\">\n  <label for=\"years\">Years since classification:</label>\n  <input id=\"years\" type=\"range\" min=\"0\" max=\"50\" value=\"0\" step=\"1\" aria-describedby=\"years-out\">\n  <output id=\"years-out\" for=\"years\">0</output>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"scales\">\n  <div class=\"scale\">\n    <span class=\"scale-label\">Risk of disclosure</span>\n    <div class=\"bar-track\">\n      <div class=\"bar-fill\" id=\"risk-bar\"></div>\n      <div class=\"threshold-line\"></div>\n      <div class=\"threshold-label\">threshold</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"scale\">\n    <span class=\"scale-label\">Cost of secrecy</span>\n    <div class=\"bar-track\">\n      <div class=\"bar-fill\" id=\"cost-bar\"></div>\n      <div class=\"threshold-line\"></div>\n      <div class=\"threshold-label\">threshold</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"decision\" id=\"decision\">\n  Status: <strong id=\"status\">Classified</strong>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"caption\" id=\"caption\">When information is fresh, the risk of disclosure is high and the cost of secrecy is low. The file stays sealed.</p>\n\n<script>\n  (function () {\n    var slider = document.getElementById('years');\n    var yearsOut = document.getElementById('years-out');\n    var riskBar = document.getElementById('risk-bar');\n    var costBar = document.getElementById('cost-bar');\n    var decision = document.getElementById('decision');\n    var status = document.getElementById('status');\n    var caption = document.getElementById('caption');\n\n    function update() {\n      var years = +slider.value;\n      yearsOut.textContent = years;\n\n      var risk = Math.max(5, 95 - (years * 1.6));\n      var cost = Math.min(95, 10 + (years * 1.5));\n\n      riskBar.style.width = risk + '%';\n      costBar.style.width = cost + '%';\n\n      var crossover = cost > 50 && risk < 50;\n\n      if (crossover) {\n        riskBar.style.backgroundColor = 'var(--teal)';\n        costBar.style.backgroundColor = 'var(--red)';\n        decision.classList.add('released');\n        status.textContent = 'Released';\n        caption.textContent = 'The cost of keeping it secret now exceeds the risk of disclosure. The threshold has flipped—the file gets released.';\n      } else if (cost > 40) {\n        riskBar.style.backgroundColor = 'var(--gold)';\n        costBar.style.backgroundColor = 'var(--gold)';\n        decision.classList.remove('released');\n        status.textContent = 'Under review';\n        caption.textContent = 'The gap is closing. Political pressure mounts, but the risk of disclosure still edges out the cost of secrecy. Not yet.';\n      } else {\n        riskBar.style.backgroundColor = 'var(--red)';\n        costBar.style.backgroundColor = 'var(--teal)';\n        decision.classList.remove('released');\n        status.textContent = 'Classified';\n        caption.textContent = 'When information is fresh, the risk of disclosure is high and the cost of secrecy is low. The file stays sealed.';\n      }\n    }\n\n    slider.addEventListener('input', update);\n    update();\n  })();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
  }
}
